      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into automotive excellence with this breathtaking find! This car is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior to the pristine interior, making it a true collector's dream. Don't miss your chance to own a vehicle that has been cared for with such incredible pride and attention!",
