    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone prioritizing utility and mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dings on the door panels, and some fading on the clear coat in sun-exposed areas. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and a few minor stains, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. It has been regularly serviced to ensure it runs well, making it a dependable choice for daily commuting or as a sturdy work vehicle. While it won't win any beauty contests, it is a solid, honest car that gets the job done.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
