      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. It has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, with every service documented and performed on schedule. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine starts instantly and runs with whisper-quiet precision, while the transmission shifts flawlessly. This is a collector-grade example that offers a like-new driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 48500.0,
