    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies reliable performance and sophisticated engineering. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure both mechanical integrity and lasting aesthetic appeal. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a superior driving experience for the discerning owner. We invite you to experience the excellence of this well-preserved automobile firsthand.",
      "price": 34900.0,
